-I knew you'd do that!
-(LAUGHS)

38:42.959 --> 38:45.119
If teenagers can be millionaires,

38:45.119 --> 38:48.119
I must be able to scrape
a few quid in clicks.

38:48.119 --> 38:52.439
Reporting. Local, national.
Wherever takes my fancy.

38:53.479 --> 38:56.559
I'm gonna vlog and
see where it gets me.

39:00.000 --> 39:01.480
(RINGS BELL)

39:07.400 --> 39:10.680
Hi there. Can I come in?

39:18.039 --> 39:21.679
Um, we've charged someone
in connection with the attack.

39:21.680 --> 39:23.480
OK.

39:24.479 --> 39:26.919
I don't think I wanna know who it is.

39:26.920 --> 39:28.440
Is it someone I know?

39:29.800 --> 39:31.880
His name's Michael Lucas.

39:31.879 --> 39:34.559
I...I don't know who that is.

39:35.600 --> 39:37.440
He goes to my school.

39:37.439 --> 39:39.599
He's the son of that cab driver.

39:39.600 --> 39:42.600
-What?!
-He's 16.

39:44.600 --> 39:47.040
We believe he was essentially
groomed into doing it

39:47.039 --> 39:49.479
by a local man named Leo Humphries.

39:49.479 --> 39:52.999
We've charged Leo alongside
Michael for your rape

39:53.000 --> 39:56.720
as well as three other,
non-recent, cases of rape.

39:56.720 --> 39:58.240
16?

39:59.280 --> 40:00.360
Yeah.

40:03.319 --> 40:06.359
Why me? Why did he rape me?
What had I done?

40:06.360 --> 40:10.320
They were at the party.
It wasn't planned. Not totally.

40:11.879 --> 40:14.759
So I was just unlucky?

40:14.759 --> 40:18.079
I'm really sorry, Trish.
But there's no doubt.

40:18.079 --> 40:19.639
We've got clear, concrete evidence.

40:19.639 --> 40:21.159
They're gonna go down for this.

40:25.639 --> 40:28.919
Well, Maggie Radcliffe
is rather a good recruiter.

40:28.920 --> 40:30.480
(CHUCKLES SOFTLY)

40:30.479 --> 40:33.199
There's a line from Hebrews
echoing through my head.

40:34.600 --> 40:38.880
"Let us all consider
how we may spur one another on

40:38.879 --> 40:43.759
"toward love and good deeds...

40:47.519 --> 40:50.599
"..not giving up meeting together,

40:50.600 --> 40:53.720
"as some are in the habit of doing...

40:55.319 --> 40:57.399
"..but encouraging one another..."

40:58.280 --> 41:02.480
Now, I hope that even without me here,

41:02.479 --> 41:05.039
you all go on encouraging one another.

41:09.519 --> 41:11.959
All any of us really want

41:11.959 --> 41:14.799
are love and good deeds.

41:19.200 --> 41:21.920
(PEOPLE CHATTER INDISTINCTLY)

41:21.920 --> 41:24.600
If I'd known you were that good,
I might have come more often.

41:24.600 --> 41:27.320
-Oh, thanks very much.
-Just ignore him. I do.

41:27.319 --> 41:29.239
-(CHUCKLES)
-Take care of yourself.

41:29.239 --> 41:31.679
You too. Both of you.

41:31.680 --> 41:34.400
See? You are loved.

41:34.400 --> 41:36.280
DAVID: Come on.

41:38.159 --> 41:40.119
Everyone's talking about your case.

41:40.119 --> 41:41.719
The fact you got them.

41:41.720 --> 41:43.600
Are they? Right.

41:43.600 --> 41:46.760
-I'm really proud of you, Dad.
-Oh, good.

41:46.759 --> 41:49.239
Really so proud.

41:55.959 --> 41:57.199
Hi, Dad.

41:58.400 --> 42:00.480
Listen, say if it's
inappropriate, but...

42:00.479 --> 42:03.359
..what if I brought
round a takeaway later?

42:03.360 --> 42:06.200
I was thinking maybe a Chinese?

42:06.200 --> 42:08.280
You know that set menu
we all used to have?

42:09.159 --> 42:10.679
Is that a rubbish idea?

42:11.959 --> 42:14.719
No. No, that could work.

42:16.519 --> 42:18.519
Great.

42:49.360 --> 42:52.320
(ALL CHATTER)

42:53.519 --> 42:57.599
You got all that?
Don't eat it all in one go!

43:43.079 --> 43:45.159
MILLER: I keep thinking
about Michael Lucas

43:45.159 --> 43:47.199
and what Leo brought him to.

43:47.200 --> 43:50.760
HARDY: He called at my house.

43:50.759 --> 43:54.039
He was one of the boys
that had photos of Daisy.

43:56.560 --> 43:58.320
That porn that Leo gave him,

43:58.319 --> 44:00.039
that's what he gave to Tom,

44:00.039 --> 44:01.559
imitating Leo.

44:02.800 --> 44:04.600
Well, not anymore.

44:08.439 --> 44:11.519
We did our job, Miller.
We got the people responsible.

44:11.519 --> 44:13.159
It's all we can do.

44:17.200 --> 44:19.360
I could do with a drink.
Do you want one?

44:19.360 --> 44:22.120
We could go to the pub!
We've never been to the pub.

44:24.600 --> 44:26.240
No.

44:26.239 --> 44:27.999
Ah.

44:33.720 --> 44:35.600
I should get back to Daisy.

44:35.600 --> 44:37.760
I should get back to my boys.

44:38.759 --> 44:41.159
So you and Daisy, then -

44:41.159 --> 44:43.319
you're gonna stay, properly, now?

44:43.319 --> 44:45.239
You don't hate it that much?

44:47.280 --> 44:49.200
I'll see you in the morning, Miller.

44:49.200 --> 44:52.440
(CHUCKLES) Fine. See you tomorrow.

45:25.319 --> 45:29.399
♪ Shall we meet in the sunrise

45:33.439 --> 45:37.359
♪ Stand one last time as two

45:41.439 --> 45:46.559
♪ I look deep into your eyes

45:49.039 --> 45:52.799
♪ Can I take my leave of you? ♪

